        "paragraph_VGX3WJ": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Our founder asked that question after watching his father, a man who'd worked hard his entire life, spend years cycling through treatments that never lasted. Chiropractors. Medications. Injections. Physical therapy appointments that cost a fortune and required time he didn't have.",
